#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:6
msgid "# `pgroonga.enable_wal` parameter"
msgstr "# `pgroonga.enable_wal`パラメーター"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:8
msgid "Since 1.1.6."
msgstr "1.1.6で追加。"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:10
msgid ""
"It's still an experimental feature. If you find a problem, please [report "
"it](https://github.com/pgroonga/pgroonga/issues/new)."
msgstr ""
"これはまだ実験的な機能です。問題を見つけた場合は[報告](https://github.com/pgroonga/pgroonga/issues/new)してください。（日本語で大丈夫です。）"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:12
msgid "## Summary"
msgstr "## 概要"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:14
msgid ""
"`pgroonga.enable_wal` parameter controls whether [WAL]({{ "
"site.postgresql_doc_base_url.en }}/runtime-config-wal.html) is enabled or "
"not."
msgstr ""
"`pgroonga.enable_wal`パラメーターは[WAL]({{ site.postgresql_doc_base_url.ja "
"}}/runtime-config-wal.html)を有効にするかどうかを制御します。"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:16
msgid ""
"PGroonga supports WAL with PostgreSQL 9.6 or later. `pgroonga.enable_wal` "
"parameter is meaningless with PostgreSQL 9.5 or earlier."
msgstr ""
"PGroongaはPostgreSQL 9.6以降で使う場合はWALをサポートしています。PostgreSQL "
"9.5以前で使う場合は`pgroonga.enable_wal`パラメーターを設定しても意味はありません。"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:18
msgid ""
"If you enable WAL support, you can use PostgreSQL's streaming replication "
"feature. See [Replication](../replication.html) for details."
msgstr ""
"WALサポートを有効にするとPostgreSQLのストリーミングレプリケーション機能を使えます。詳細は[レプリケーション](../replication.html)を参照してください。"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:20
msgid ""
"If you enable WAL support, update performance will be decreased because some"
" extra disk writes are needed."
msgstr "WALサポートを有効にすると更新性能が落ちるはずです。これは追加のディスク書き込みが必要になるからです。"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:22
msgid ""
"The default value is `off`. It means that PGroonga doesn't generate WAL even"
" when you're using PostgreSQL 9.6 or later. It'll be `on` by default when "
"this feature is marked as stable."
msgstr ""
"デフォルト値は`off`です。これは、PGroongaはPostgreSQL "
"9.6以降で使っている場合でもWALを生成しないということです。この機能が安定したらデフォルトで`on`になる予定です。"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:24
msgid "## Syntax"
msgstr "## 構文"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:26
msgid "In SQL:"
msgstr "SQLの場合："

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:28
msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SET pgroonga.enable_wal = boolean;\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:32
msgid "In `postgresql.conf`:"
msgstr "`postgresql.conf`の場合："

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:34
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"pgroonga.enable_wal = boolean\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:38
msgid ""
"`boolean` is a boolean value. There are some literals for boolean value such"
" as `on`, `off`, `true`, `false`, `yes` and `no`."
msgstr ""
"`boolean`は真偽値です。真偽値には`on`、`off`、`true`、`false`、`yes`、`no`のようなリテラルがあります。"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:40
msgid "## Usage"
msgstr "## 使い方"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:42
msgid "Here is an example SQL to enable WAL support:"
msgstr "以下はWALサポートを有効にするSQLの例です。"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:44
msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SET pgroonga.enable_wal = on;\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:48
msgid "Here is an example configration to enable WAL support:"
msgstr "以下はWALサポートを有効にする設定の例です。"

#: ../../../../../v1/reference/parameters/enable-wal.md:50
msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"pgroonga.enable_wal = on\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

